# Root .dockerignore — applies to every build whose context is the repo
# root (currently both apps/api/Dockerfile and apps/web/Dockerfile).
#
# Each entry shrinks the build context that gets COPYed into the daemon
# and protects against accidentally baking secrets or local-only state
# into the image.

# Dependencies — reinstalled fresh in the builder stage.
**/node_modules

# Build outputs — regenerated inside the build.
**/dist
**/.angular
**/.next
**/.nest
**/coverage
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
**/tsconfig.build.tsbuildinfo

# Local-only env files — DATABASE_URL etc. come from docker-compose.
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# Editor / OS noise.
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# VCS — not needed to build runtime artifacts.
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# Docker artifacts — avoid recursive copies.
**/Dockerfile
**/docker-compose*.yml
**/.dockerignore

# Docs.
README.md
**/*.md
